{"tid":2118158,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【7‧21核彈】《蘋果》獲內部通訊　證指揮官令警員「死守」元朗警署　勿理999報案","createTime":"2020-07-21T09:47:45.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-21T10:11:43.000Z","uid":6497,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"05599efef560bedf91d9b7c777a01b50ffce41f0","tid":2118158,"uid":6497,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T09:47:45.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/rMGEM2m3z-0LbGmqsn3by1L9OvQ=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RF5OGKV3ZHZBO5Y3PODXN4NVMA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FrMGEM2m3z-0LbGmqsn3by1L9OvQ%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRF5OGKV3ZHZBO5Y3PODXN4NVMA.jpg&h=d4628637&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200721/US2VORAJ4RJJXPJMFXEYXZUZME/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200721%2FUS2VORAJ4RJJXPJMFXEYXZUZME%2F&d=PhzZiar3PrZ%2B4r6hY23Rj04axDeVXns42j9POfnWuxs%3D&h=5c4dcb98\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200721%2FUS2VORAJ4RJJXPJMFXEYXZUZME%2F&h=972cf874\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200721/US2VORAJ4RJJXPJMFXEYXZUZME/</a><br />\n<br />\n元朗白衣人恐襲一周年，更多短片和證據曝光。網上近日再次流傳當晚元朗警署內短片 ，顯示大批市民到場要求警方出動，但十多名警員不為所動，隨後更落閘關閉警署。根據《蘋果》近日取得的警方內部通訊紀錄，元朗區指揮官曾指示所有人員在元朗警署戒備，不會處理任何999報案的案件，情況與警員「死守」警署脗合。警方初時否認曾作相關指示，又稱匿名指控屬惡意捏造；惟記者原句引述警方紀錄後，警方始承認當晚元朗警署及天水圍警署被包圍後，曾指示其他巡邏人員立刻返回警署候命。"},{"pid":"e17f225db18f8ad5b364a9da5ab6f38fe1ddaa19","tid":2118158,"uid":286209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T09:48:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7b7e01a8479dfa63cb7cf722f24e584660eeb08","tid":2118158,"uid":27520,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-21T09:49:50.000Z","msg":"又核彈<img src=\"/assets/faces/nor